 &amp;\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Lab Part\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Mikrocontroller Fundamentals\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Elektronik 1\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Linear Algebra\n\nSemester 3\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Mathematik 2\n &amp;\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Edited HSLU-Formulary\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Elektronik 2\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Signale &amp; Systeme\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Advanced Programming\n\nSemester 4\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Advanced Embedded Systems\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Digital Design\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Leistungselektronik &amp; Elektrische Antriebe\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Nachrichtentechnik\n /\n\n  \n  \n  \n    File\n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  Regelungstechnik\n\n","id":"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/downloads/","title":"Download"},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/photos/":{"body":"Not sure how to do this, might think up of something. For now you can check out my flickr profile: \n  \n  Flickr\n\n","id":"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/photos/","title":"Photos"},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/projects/":{"body":"Summaries 📚\nBachelor – Electrical Engineering\nI'm up for sharing all my summaries for the different courses. If they're useful to you, then that's good! I want to contribute somehow to open education and hopefully this helps.\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    Semester 1\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    My summaries from my first semester of the bachelor of electrical engineering at HSLU Lucerne.\n  \n  \n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    Semester 2\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    My summaries from my second semester of the bachelor of electrical engineering at HSLU Lucerne.\n  \n  \n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    Semester 3\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    My summaries from my third semester of the bachelor of electrical engineering at HSLU Lucerne.\n  \n  \n    \n    \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    Semester 4\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    My summaries from my fourth semester of the bachelor of electrical engineering at HSLU Lucerne.\n  \n  \n    \n    \n  \n\nBikepacking 🚲\n\nGenau wenn man irgendwo im nirgendwo ist, die Regenkleider völlig durchnässt und das Ziel viel zu weit weg gesetzt hat, dann erlebt man das Abenteuer.\n\nMe!\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n    Suisse de Tour\n  \n  \n  \n    A four week tour I've done during the summer of 2021. I explored my home country thoroughly by visiting all the main cities of each canton.\n  \n  \n    \n    Tour-Report (🇩🇪)\n    \n    \n    /\n    Photos\n    \n  \n\n","id":"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/projects/","title":"Projects"},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/search/":{"body":"\n  \n  \n      \n      \n  \n\n\n","id":"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/search/","title":"Search"},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/writing/":{"body":"Once in a lifetime I might write something, could it be for friends or just food for thought. It'll show up here with the respective category and by year (so it's easier to find). For grammar mistakes and horrible opinions, write me in some shape or form (except you know, a letter bomb or other malicious methods).\n","id":"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/writing/","title":"Writing"}},"docInfo":{"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/":{"body":34,"title":3},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/downloads/":{"body":97,"title":1},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/photos/":{"body":10,"title":1},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/projects/":{"body":110,"title":1},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/search/":{"body":0,"title":1},"https://joelvonrotz.github.io/writing/":{"body":30,"title":1}},"length":6},"lang":"English"}